  "description": "This is not just any meatball. It's a giant, succulent, cheddar-stuffed meatball, nestled in a rich puddle of warm tomato broth with couscous (giant, of course!). Topped with a smattering of fresh basil, this feel-good dish is a sure-fire hit. Mighty, meaty, utterly moreish!",
